snippet: Fistfights broke out between ultranationalist Japanese shouting anti-Korean slogans and counterprotesters on the streets of Tokyo, where public violence is rare.
abstract: Eight people are arrested on streets of Tokyo after fistfights break out between ultra-nationalist Japanese shouting anti-Korean slogans and counter-protesters.
lead_paragraph: Fistfights broke out between ultranationalist Japanese shouting anti-Korean slogans and counterprotesters on the streets of Tokyo, where public violence is rare.

headline.main: 8 Arrested in Tokyo Fights Involving Anti-Korean Group
